## 9. Rollback Plan

See: [Deployment Guide — Section 8](DPG-v1.0-KSA-2.docx)

**Rollback Decision Criteria:** - Extension crashes VS Code on startup → Immediate unpublish - Commands throw unhandled errors → Publish previous version - Extension fails to activate silently → Hotfix patch

**Estimated Rollback Time:** ~20 minutes

